excerpt: 'In this paper we present a general framework for estimating regression models subject to a user-defined level of fairness. We do that using ridge regression, which is flexible, has already tons of literature and in general simplifies a lot the estimation. [See paper here](https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11222-022-10143-w)'
